Answer.feedback: Thanks for the opportunity to participate and good luck with your research!   My strategy was to look at the total "benefit" across group apple, group bee and group cow - and the proposal that offered the greatest benefit would also provide the best compromise as long as two of the three groups experienced significant benefits as a result of the proposal.   The only other feedback I might have is that the readability of the study might be easier if the options for group apple, group bee and group cow were listed using bullet format.   Thanks again!
